---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="Privacy Policy — EMPIRIA Advisory">
<header id="header">
  <div class="header-inner">
    <a href="/" class="logo" aria-label="EMPIRIA Advisory home">
      <span class="logo-mark">E</span>
      <span class="logo-text">EMPIRIA <em>Advisory</em></span>
    </a>
    <a href="/" class="back-link">← Back to Home</a>
  </div>
</header>
<main class="legal-page">
  <div class="container">
    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="meta">Last updated: June 2025</p>
    <div class="legal-body">
      <h2>1. Overview</h2>
      <p>EMPIRIA Advisory operates this website in accordance with privacy-by-design principles. We collect only the data strictly necessary for website functionality and security. We do not use advertising trackers, behavioural profiling technologies, or third-party analytics.</p>
      <h2>2. Data We Collect</h2>
      <p>We may collect the following limited categories of data: (a) technical data automatically transmitted by your browser for the purpose of serving web pages (IP address, browser type, referring page), retained only in server logs for security purposes and deleted on a rolling 30-day basis; (b) contact information you voluntarily provide when initiating a consultation enquiry via email.</p>
      <h2>3. Legal Basis</h2>
      <p>Where applicable under GDPR, our processing is based on: legitimate interests (server security logging); and consent (where you proactively contact us).</p>
      <h2>4. Data Sharing</h2>
      <p>We do not sell, rent, or share personal data with third parties for commercial purposes. Data may be disclosed where required by applicable law.</p>
      <h2>5. Your Rights</h2>
      <p>Under GDPR and applicable data protection law, you have the right to access, rectify, erase, restrict, or object to processing of your personal data. To exercise these rights, contact: advisor@empiriadvisory.com</p>
      <h2>6. Contact</h2>
      <p>Data controller: EMPIRIA Advisory<br/>Email: advisor@empiriadvisory.com</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</main>
</Layout>
<style>
:root {
  --slate-900: #0B0F19;
  --accent: #4A7FCC;
  --off-white: #F0EDE6;
  --muted: #7A8EA8;
  --border: rgba(74, 127, 204, 0.15);
}
.container { max-width: 760px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 2rem; }
#header { padding: 1.25rem 0; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); }
.header-inner { max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 2rem; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; }
.logo { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.625rem; text-decoration: none; }
.logo-mark { width: 28px; height: 28px; background: var(--accent); color: white; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-family: serif; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 700; border-radius: 2px; }
.logo-text { font-size: 0.9375rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--off-white); letter-spacing: 0.05em; text-transform: uppercase; }
.logo-text em { font-style: normal; font-weight: 300; color: var(--muted); }
.back-link { font-size: 0.875rem; color: var(--muted); text-decoration: none; }
.back-link:hover { color: var(--off-white); }
.legal-page { padding: 5rem 0; }
h1 { font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 2.5rem; font-weight: 500; color: var(--off-white); margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
.meta { font-family: monospace; font-size: 0.8125rem; color: var(--muted); margin-bottom: 3rem; }
.legal-body h2 { font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 1.125rem; font-weight: 500; color: var(--off-white); margin-top: 2rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }
.legal-body p { font-size: 0.9375rem; color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.75; }
</style>
